    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Eriteus">Eriteo</name></persName> filio <persName>bone
                            memorie <name ref="Ermiteus">Ermitei</name></persName> permuta beni con
                            <persName ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName> gratia
                        Dei huius Sancte Lucane ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>
                        (…). Eriteo cede a Gherardo quatuor <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Wine">petie de terra et vinee</rs> mee
                        ille, quas abeo <placeName ref="#places/555"
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Wine #Fiscal_property #Mention"
                            >in loco prope <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/219" key="#Churches">Sancti
                                Prosperi</orgName></placeName>, qui una ex ipse petia de terra <rs
                            key="#Confinia">est tenentes uno capu</rs> in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/283">Sancti Petri, ubi dicitur
                        Sumaldi</orgName>, alio capu tene in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention">terra <persName
                                key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions" ref="#people/3308"
                                >Eribrandi</persName></rs>, lato uno tene in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Mintus"
                                >Minti</name></persName> et in aliquantulo in <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vinea</rs>, qui fuit <persName key="#Confinia #Wine" ref="#people/211"
                            >quondam T[eu]dimundi</persName>, alio lato tene in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> qui fuit <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">quondam <name ref="Donnus"
                                >Doni</name></persName>; petia ipsa de terra in integrum; et ille
                        alia secunda petia de terra est tenentes uno capu in via publica, alio caput
                        tene in <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Wine"><name ref="Mintus">Minti</name></persName>,
                        lato uno tene in <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> suprascripte <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/219" key="#Confinia #Wine #Churches">Sancti
                            Prosperi</orgName>, alio lato tene in <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terra</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions" ref="#people/147"
                            >Lamberti</persName>, petia ipsa de terra in integrum; et ille petia de
                        vinea <placeName key="#Confinia #Wine">ubi dicitur a Polic[…]</placeName>,
                        qui uno capu est tenentes in <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        suprascripti <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name
                                ref="Mintus">Minti</name></persName>, et alio capu est tenente in
                        terra mea qui supra Eriteo, lato uno tene in <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terra</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Cuneradus"
                                >Chuneradi</name></persName> et in aliquantulo in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> suprascripti episcopatui vestro, et
                        alio lato tene in vinea <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name
                                ref="Walfredus">Vualdifridi</name></persName>, petia ipsa de vinea
                        in integrum; et ille alia petia de vinea et orto est tenente uno capu cum
                        uno lato in terra ipsius ecclesie Sancti Prosperi, et alio capu tene in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fruits/vegetables">terra et orto</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/242">Sancti Petri,</orgName> que <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Deacons #rectorOf" ref="#people/3314"
                            >Daiprando</persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diacono</rs> modo ad manus suas [abere]a videtur, lato
                        uno tene in <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs> et aliquantulo in terra
                        suprascripti M[inti]; suprascripte quatuor petie de terra et vinee (…) una
                        cum fossis et cesis et omnibus arboribus suis (…) et sunt per mensura a
                        iusta perticha mensurata modiorum <rs key="#Size">quinque et sistariorum
                            viginti</rs>. (…) Riceve in cambio una <rs key="#Petiae #Wine">petia de
                            vinea</rs> in loco <placeName ref="#places/166"
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Wine #Roads">Tempaniano</placeName>
                        prope casa abitationis mee, pertenentes suprascripte <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/219" key="#Churches">Sancti
                            Prosperi</orgName>, que est de suppotestatem ipsius <rs
                            key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> vestro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, et est tenente uno capu cum uno lato in terra mea qui
                        supra Eriteo et aliquantulo in <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Petrus"
                                >Petri</name></persName> de filio <persName>quondam <name
                                ref="Aricausus">Aricausi</name></persName>, alio capu tene in <rs
                            key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, et alio lato tene in classo; suprascripta
                        petia de vinea (…) una cum fossis et cesis et omnibus arboribus suis (…);
                        seo et (…) una petia de terra in suprascripto loco similiter prope case
                        abitationis mee, et pertinens ecclesie Sancti Prosperi; predicta petia de
                        terra est tenente uno capu cum uno lato in <rs key="#Roads">via
                        publica</rs>, alio capu tene in <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs> ipsius <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/219" key="#Confinia #Wine #Churches">Sancti
                            Prosperi</orgName>, quas in tua reservasti potestatem, et alio lato tene
                        in <rs key="#Casalini/fundamenta #Landed_possessions">terra et in fundamento
                            de casa</rs> de <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Casalini/fundamenta #Landed_possessions">filii quondam
                                <name ref="Ermiteus">Ermitei</name></persName>: predicta petia de
                        terra (…) cum cesis et fossis et omnibus arboribus suis (…) est per mensura
                        a iusta perticha mensurata <rs key="#Size">modiorum quinque</rs>. Ubi et
                        super hanc commutationem tu qui supra <persName ref="#people/214"
                            key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> direxisti <rs
                            key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Bishops">missos tuos</rs>,
                        idest <persName key="#Witness #Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Deacons"
                                ><name ref="Sigelfredus">Sichalfridi </name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diacono</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Priests"><name
                                ref="Gundiprandus">Gudiprando</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> seu et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Priests"><name
                                ref="Viventius">Viventius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs>; et <persName ref="#people/1514"
                            key="#Marquis/duke">Adalbertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> diresit <rs
                            key="#Marquis/duke #Missus_of_other_public_authorities">misos suos</rs>,
                        idest <persName key="#Witness #Missus_of_other_public_authorities"><name
                                ref="Aufridus/de Wamo">Aufridi de <placeName ref="#places/179"
                                    >Vuamo</placeName></name></persName>, qui ambulaverunt et
                        previderunt adque vobis renuntiaverunt quod melioratum cambio (…). Pena in
                        duplum. <persName key="#Writer #Witness #Notary"><name ref="Lopo"
                                >Lopo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs key="#Commutatio"
                            >cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            key="#Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops">Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Oltre ai missi sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>:
                            <persName key="#Witness #Scabini"><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                                >Ildiprando</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Scabini">schabinus</rs>, <persName ref="#people/147"
                            key="#Witness">Lamberto</persName>, <persName ref="#people/150"
                            key="#Witness">Fraolmi</persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                            >[………]do</persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudemundus"
                                >Teudimundus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Liutfredus">Liutifridi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudebertus">Teupertus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        <persName>qd. <name ref="Ermiteus">Ermitei</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness">[teste sconosciuto]</persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
